ntent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 14/6.\r\n</h2><h2>M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp Los Blancos v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70-80 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai David De Gea &ndash; m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng n\u0103m c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n K\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 146 MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 146 MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-MU-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/6: Real chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">heo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp Hector Cuper, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah &ldquo;g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 100% k\u1ecbp ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay&rdquo;. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c nhanh h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho \u0110T v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Ai C\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ee5 Martial</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ph\u00e1p x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Martial.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FA c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n 2 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t trong 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i cho t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, khi Arsenal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery trinh bay ro viec tan dung nhung cai ten san co.\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y r\u00f5 vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1eb5n c\u00f3.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/unai-emery-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea ngay 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay, Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n&rdquo; c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha &ndash; HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft &ldquo;s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&rdquo; v\u1edbi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n sa th\u1ea3i sau khi \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi Los Blancos, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3624","checkdouble":"188496"},{"date":"18:16 14/06","title":"Chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/real-madrid-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi thay Navas. David de Gea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Zidane, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a De Gea v\u1ec1 Bernabeu.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-80-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLopetegui t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft De Gea v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U21 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, trong th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T TBN \u00f4ng c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n \u01b0u ti\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c De Gea \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real Madrid.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Mundo Deportivo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Roma.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1992, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Alisson k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real, anh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real ph\u1ea3i chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo Mundo Deportivo, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ederson \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Alisson\" title=\"thu mon Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/real-madrid-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Alisson \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, anh s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu sau khi h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Selecao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEderson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Navas.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nho-thuyet-khach-liverpool-sap-co-thu-mon-moi-172-187344.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Alisson</span>, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Roma y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil khi \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3623","checkdouble":"188491"},{"date":"18:32 14/06","title":"Messi: \u201cBarca c\u1ea7n Griezmann \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/messi-barca-can-griezmann-de-thong-tri-chau-au.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 Catalonia trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan-180-188470.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Antoine Griezmann</span> kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Atletico Madrid trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u Euro, sau nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5p th\u1ecfm chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf v\u00e0 b\u1ea1t ng\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi n\u0103m qua \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 chi\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00ec t\u00ecnh ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1ecb FIFA c\u1ea5m chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Griezmann \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C\u00fap C1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Griezmann \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C\u00fap C1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/messi-moi-goi-griezmann-den-voi-barcelona.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Griezmann: \"Barca c\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League\"</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1ee3ng phong h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 Man Utd m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh Barcelona. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i, k\u00e9o theo h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn anh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou t\u1eeb n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Luis Suarez hay hai \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ousmane Dembele v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Leo Messi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Griezmann s\u1edbm v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u1ec1 tham v\u1ecdng t\u00e1i th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u1ee7a Barca sau khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Real Sociedad trong tay:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Griezmann th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League th\u00eam n\u1eefa v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Griezmann c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barca hay kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB, anh bi\u1ebft c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Messi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Griezmann. Hai ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu hai \u0110TQG v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec so le nhau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-da-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-180-188330.html\">Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u01b0ng\u2026</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan-180-188470.html\">Griezmann l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai... nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chu-tich-la-liga-bao-tin-vui-cho-thanh-madrid-tin-buon-cho-barca-180-188224.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga b\u00e1o tin vui cho th\u00e0nh Madrid, tin bu\u1ed3n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3622","checkdouble":"188495"},{"date":"05:28 15/06","title":"Lopetegui b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Nga vs Saudi Arabia, th\u00ec t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o quan tr\u1ecdng ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Julen Lopetegui.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u1edf m\u00e0n bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez n\u00f3i: \"Th\u1ef1c ra, Cch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y sau khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> k\u1ebft th\u00fac, khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh quang. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp x\u1ea3y ra m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y qua, th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edf ra trang m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \"Madridista\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Real k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra v\u1edbi Lopetegui t\u1ea1i Madrid.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft Real v\u00e0 n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft Real v\u00e0 n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Real-Madrid-present-new-coach-Julen-Lopetegui.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Lopetegui. \u1ea2nh: Reuters.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Lopetegui cho bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n HLV t\u1ea1i Bernabeu: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft n\u00f3i: \u201cSau khi m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i qua \u0111\u1eddi, vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn tin b\u1ecb \u0110TQG sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u1ea5t\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do sa th\u1ea3i li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan g\u00ec t\u1edbi l\u00fd do chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n hay kh\u00f4ng, Lopetegui t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 cho hay kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7n \u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Rubiales (ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN) h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ki\u1ec3u kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n trung th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn (gia nh\u1eadp Real) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng khai v\u00e0 che gi\u1ea5u n\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 trung th\u1ef1c h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\", Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \"Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch cho r\u1eb1ng Real \u0111\u00e3 \"\u0103n tr\u1ed9m\" Lopetegui v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00f4 l\u00ed. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3621","checkdouble":"188509"},{"date":"06:04 15/06","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n CLB c\u1ee7a Griezmann m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/griezmann-da-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u00e2m ran</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi trong nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng qua. T\u1eeb l\u00fac b\u00e1o ch\u00ed khui ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, Barcelona l\u00e0 s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Griezmann v\u00e0 s\u1ebd mang anh v\u1ec1 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2018 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 Barca t\u1eebng mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng qua video h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng qua video h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/Griezmann-da-cong-bo-tuong-lai-cua-minh-thong-qua-video-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League v\u1edbi Atletico, Griezmann b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u suy t\u00ednh l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n HLV Diego Simeone c\u00f9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. N\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho t\u1edbi c\u00e1ch th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh. Trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, Griezmann b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i hay \u1edf nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann va video\" title=\"Griezmann va video\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Griezmann-va-video.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ed9t c\u1ea3nh trong video c\u1ee7a Griezmann</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Griezmann kho\u00e1c t\u1ea5m \u00e1o \u0111en c\u00f3 m\u0169 tr\u00f9m \u0111\u1ee9ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng le l\u00f3i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u00e1nh \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea7m t\u01b0 nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e2u xa l\u1ea1, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Wanda Metropolitano c\u1ee7a Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho Atletico ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 n\u0103m 2019. H\u1ecd \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap-421-188449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap-421-188449.html\">Griezmann l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i ca \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u00edt ng\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh - sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-griezmann-se-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-188443.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/mbappe-griezmann-se-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-griezmann-se-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-188443.html\">Mbappe: Griezmann s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>Kylian Mbappe ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico Madrid s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3620","checkdouble":"188510"},{"date":"06:54 15/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Barca n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Griezmann \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/17/nguoi-barca-noi-gi-ve-viec-griezmann-o-lai-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Anh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barcelona trong th\u1eddi gian qua s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Griezmann \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt trong th\u1eddi gian qua. V\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Atletico Madrid ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, Barcelona l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1o li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Griezmann b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi ph\u1ea1m quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (FIFA). Nghe \u0111\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Pique-phat-bieu-ve-Griezmann-va-quyet-dinh-o-lai-Atletico-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t video</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/antoine-griezmann-da-cong-bo-tuong-lai-180-188510.html\" target=\"_blank\">quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Griezmann</span> l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. Anh m\u1edbi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t b\u1edfi c\u00f4ng ty \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Kosmos c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pique ch\u00fac Griezmann may m\u1eafn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin tr\u00ean, Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Anh c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Kosmos ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111o\u1ea1n video n\u00f3i tr\u00ean. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean ch\u00fac Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann ghi ban cho Atletico truoc Marseille\" title=\"Griezmann ghi ban cho Atletico truoc Marseille\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/griezmann-cong-bo-tuong-lai-ngay-trong-tuan-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>M\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o c\u1ee7a Griezmann trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</em>\u201d, Pique vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>C\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Kosmos Studios v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Griezmann trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n qua. Anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Griezmann gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung cho World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Les Blues s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Australia v\u00e0o 17h ng\u00e0y 16/6 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-barca-can-griezmann-de-vo-dich-champions-league-180-188495.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/messi-barca-can-griezmann-de-thong-tri-chau-au.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-barca-can-griezmann-de-vo-dich-champions-league-180-188495.html\">Messi: \u201cBarca c\u1ea7n Griezmann \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League\u201d</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 Catalonia trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan-180-188470.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/27/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan-180-188470.html\">Griezmann l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai... nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griemann th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i d\u1eddi l\u1ea1i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3619","checkdouble":"188517"}]}